	<description>The Corpus embody the cold vacuum of space - heartless and bent on taking anything left unprotected.\n\nDriven by profits, the Corpus Boardâ€™s small numbers are supplemented by their legion of robot proxies, optimized for quick and efficient destruction.</description>
    <leaderTitle>profit master</leaderTitle>
	<label>corpus conglomerate</label>
